accessibility.text: Visuals are only mood references,  original content will be designed.

The special offers and announcements can appear in many different forms, for example 3D bubbles of information or amorphous forms filled with video content in the foreground of main visualizations. They can bloom out as a flowers revealing something special inside, unwrap as a gift boxes, open as a secret door, appear out of smoke or flowing water etc.
